details.description: A public notice for correction in particulars for the National Eligibility-cum-Entrance Test (NEET (UG)) - 2025 examination.
details.deadline: The window for corrections shall be available till 11 March 2025 (up to 11:50 P.M.).
details.fees: In cases where changes affect the fee amount, candidates will be charged any excess fee accordingly. Please note that any excess payments made will not be refunded.
details.contact_info: For further clarification related to NEET (UG) - 2025, the candidates can also contact helpdesk in person or at 011-40759000/011-69227700 or email at neetug2025@nta.ac.in.
